title: Married At First Sight S01 Preview And Casting Special
description:
Married at First Sight on FYITM is an extreme social experiment that follows six people who agree to a provocative proposal: getting legally married the moment they first meet. Four specialists Ã¢â‚¬â€œ sexologist Dr. Logan Levkoff, spiritualist Greg Epstein, psychologist Dr. Joseph Cilona and sociologist Dr. Pepper Schwartz Ã¢â‚¬â€œ create what they believe are three perfect couples based on scientific matchmaking. Based on a hit Danish show, Married at First Sight follows the classic lifestyle stories of newlyweds, from the honeymoon to early nesting to other events of married life. After several weeks together, each couple must make a decision: do they remain together or decide to separate?

Married At First Sight: Casting Special
Released Jul 08, 2014
This is an in depth look at the casting process for this ground breaking social experiment, where a team of relationship experts, set out to arrange three marriages. If the experts succeed the couples will not meet until their wedding ceremony. Once married the couples will live together, legally bound, for five weeks before deciding if they want to stay married or get a divorce. This hour long special will introduce the experiment, the four experts and determine whether anyone will be brave enough to participate.
